    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The \"evolving with new data\" angle is okay, but the reporters are going to smell that a mile away. They're literally going to ask if the candidate is just changing their mind because the donor interests changed. If we say \"new data,\" they'll ask exactly what data changed between last month and today. Do we actually have any new economic reports we can point to, or are we just spinning this?",
